[{"c":"<p>I've found the pearl of greatest price,</p><p>My heart doth sing for joy:</p><p>And sing I must, a Christ I have;</p><p>O what a Christ have I?</p>"},{"c":"<p>Christ is the Way, the Truth, the Life,</p><p>The way to God on high,</p><p>Life to the dead, the truth of types,</p><p>The truth of prophesy.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Christ is a prophet, priest and king,</p><p>A Prophet full of light,</p><p>A Priest that stands 'twixt God and man,</p><p>A King that rules with might.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Christ's manhood is a temple, where</p><p>The altar God doth rest;</p><p>My Christ, he is the sacrifice,</p><p>My Christ he is the priest.</p>"},{"c":"<p>My Christ he is the Lord of lords,</p><p>He is the King of kings;</p><p>He is the Sun of righteousness,</p><p>With healing in his wings.</p>"},{"c":"<p>My Christ, he is the Tree of Life,</p><p>Which in God's garden grows;</p><p>Whose fruit does feed, whose leaves do heal;</p><p>My Christ is Sharon's rose.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Christ is my meat, Christ is my drink,</p><p>My physic and my health,</p><p>My peace, my strength, my joy, my crown,</p><p>My glory and my wealth.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Christ is my father, and my friend,</p><p>My brother and my love;</p><p>My head, my hope, my counselor,</p><p>My advocate above.</p>"},{"c":"<p>My Christ, he is the Heaven of heavens,</p><p>My Christ what shall I call?</p><p>My Christ is first, my Christ is last,</p><p>My Christ is all in all.</p>"}]